<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Campus Life</title>
  <style>
    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(to right, #2c3e50, #3498db);
      color: #fff;
      padding: 20px;
    }

    header {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 2em 1em;
      background: linear-gradient(to right, #1e3c72, #2a5298);
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }

    header h1 {
      font-size: 2em;
    }

    .content {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 20px;
    }

    .text-section {
      font-size: 1.2em;
      margin-bottom: 1em;
    }

    .box-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
      gap: 20px;
    }

    .box {
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
      color: #000;
      background-color: #fff;
    }

    .box.blue {
      background-color: #a9c9ff;
    }

    .box.yellow {
      background-color: #ffd179;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      header h1 {
        font-size: 1.5em;
      }

      .text-section {
        font-size: 1em;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <header>
    <h1>Campus Life</h1>
  </header>

  <div class="content">
    <div class="text-section">
      <p>
        At our school, we strive to provide our students with an exceptional educational experience that goes beyond traditional learning. Here are some of the features that set us apart:
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="box-grid">
      <div class="box blue">
        We maintain a school-like discipline that fosters a sense of order and respect in our students, preparing them for success in all aspects of life.
      </div>
      <div class="box yellow">
        Our teaching is of such high quality that private coaching is unnecessary. From day one, our students receive comprehensive orientation for entrance exams along with routine teaching.
      </div>
      <div class="box blue">
        We also offer personality development classes, limited holidays, and a “home away from home” hostel facility for both boys and girls, ensuring that our students are well-rounded and happy.
      </div>
      <div class="box yellow">
        Our chapter-wise tests are designed to follow CHSE and entrance patterns, providing our students with a thorough understanding of the subject matter and the necessary skills to succeed.
      </div>
      <div class="box blue">
        Our faculty is highly qualified and friendly, creating a supportive and collaborative learning environment that is in tune with students’ needs, similar to that of western countries.
      </div>
      <div class="box yellow">
        We recognize that education is not just about academics, which is why we offer yoga, spiritualism, cultural programs, and memory sharpening quiz programs as part of our routine.
      </div>
      <div class="box blue">
        We believe in personal attention, and our highly qualified teachers provide individualized support to each student to help them reach their full potential.
      </div>
      <div class="box yellow">
        In the next two years, we will be fully air-conditioning our classrooms and providing modern amenities to create a comfortable and conducive learning environment.
    </div>
    <div class="box blue">
        We recognize that not all students come from an English medium background, which is why we offer bridge courses from Oriya to English and communicative English courses for Oriya medium students. We also provide special orientation classes in mathematics for English medium students.
    </div>
  </div>

</body>
</html>
